UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 550
1 A RESOLUTION confirming the appointment of Kenton W. Bottoms II to the Fish
2 and Wildlife Resources Commission.
3 WHEREAS, on December 16, 2025, in accordance with KRS 150.022 and by virtue
4 of Executive Order 2025-843, Governor Andy Beshear appointed Kenton W. Bottoms II
5 to the Fish and Wildlife Resources Commission for a term expiring December 31, 2028;
6 and
7 WHEREAS, the appointment is subject to Senate confirmation; and
8 WHEREAS, Kenton W. Bottoms II has been determined to meet the requirements
9 of KRS 150.022, representing the Sixth Commission District;
10 NOW, THEREFORE,
11 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
12 Kentucky:
13 Section 1. The Senate hereby confirms the appointment of Kenton W. Bottoms
14 II to the Fish and Wildlife Resources Commission.
15 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall forward a copy of this Resolution and
16 notification of its adoption to Kenton W. Bottoms II of Lawrenceburg, Anderson County,
17 Kentucky, and to Governor Andy Beshear, 703 Capital Avenue, Room 133, Frankfort,
18 Kentucky 40601.
